room_title: Escape room "The Mischevious Elves" by Ocean State Escape in Providence
room_description: The elves have gone a little overboard with their pranks this year! By locking up the Naughty & Nice list, they have drained the Christmas spirit! They have left puzzles, riddles and clues for you to solve to find it. Can you find the list and restore the Christmas spirit before time runs out?
